data.description: SELLERS OFFERING HOME WARRANTY! Discover the charm of Fort Payne, Alabama in this inviting 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, conveniently located in a peaceful neighborhood. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light, courtesy of the energy-efficient windows installed less than 5 years ago. The spacious backyard, surrounded by a privacy fence, is an entertainer's dream, offering stunning mountain views that provide the perfect space for gatherings and relaxation. Upgrades to major systems, including the HVAC, hot water heater, and roof, were completed within the last 5 years, ensuring your peace of mind. Additionally, a walk-in crawl space provides ample storage. Schedule your private showing today!
